  <!-- EN: Feral Plate Armour -->
  <Slag_Plate_Crude.label>蛮族板甲</Slag_Plate_Crude.label>
  <!-- EN: Constructed of recycled slag, this plate armour is encumbering but effective against bludgeoning. The gaps in the plates render it almost useless against animals, bullets, or fire. It's made of metal, so don't get electrocuted while wearing this. -->
  <Slag_Plate_Crude.description>这种板甲由回收的矿渣制成，虽然笨重，但却能有效抵御重击。板子上的缝隙使它对动物攻击、子弹射击和火炎灼烧几乎毫无抵御能力。它是由金属片粗制成的，所以这东西是导电的。</Slag_Plate_Crude.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Spiked Feral Plate Armour -->
  <Slag_Plate_Improved.label>尖刺蛮族板甲</Slag_Plate_Improved.label>
  <!-- EN: An improvement of the crude slag plate armour, it's very effective in gunfights. Flexible joints allow reduced encumbrance. Spikes and paint increase the wearer's badassitude by a factor of +2! -->
  <Slag_Plate_Improved.description>蛮族板甲的改进型，对抗枪击更加有效。灵活的关节可以减少负重。尖刺和油漆使穿戴者的匪徒气质+2！</Slag_Plate_Improved.description>
  
